Make a plan for words like   :

 Day = Duvha
 Duvha = sun
 but Sun != day 

 Invitation = Thambo
Thambo = Rope

Rope != Invitation




"Hello-male": ["Nnda!"],
    "Hello-Female)": ["Aa!"],

    "good morning-start": ["NDI MATSHELONI"],
    "good afternoon-start": ["NDI MASIARI"],
    "good evening": ["NDI MADEKWANA"],
    "good morning-response": ["NDI MATSHELONI AVHUDI"],
    "good afternoon-response": ["NDI MASIARI AVHUDI"],
